# TC10: ChargeBattery3
# Precondition setup: power ON, BoostMode, battery below full
# Action: start charging
# Expected: no change because BoostMode cannot charge.
# NOTE: BoostMode setup requires dust event implementation or the corresponding PR.
power
battery 50
start
dust
expect power on
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect battery 50
charge
expect charging off
expect battery 50
expect mode BoostMode
expect motor moving
expect motorForward true
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
exit
